snippet.title: UFL™ Open Beta Announcement Trailer | June 7-9
snippet.description:
⚡️ Charge your gamepads!
⠀
𝗨𝗙𝗟 𝗢𝗽𝗲𝗻 𝗕𝗲𝘁𝗮 is happening on June 7-9.
Don't miss out on the opportunity to play early and provide valuable feedback!
⠀
𝗣𝗿𝗲-𝗗𝗼𝘄𝗻𝗹𝗼𝗮𝗱 is available now:
👉 PlayStation 5: https://ufl.link/PS5
👉 Xbox Series X|S: https://ufl.link/Xbox
⠀
𝗙𝗼𝗹𝗹𝗼𝘄 our social channels ⬇️
Discord: https://ufl.link/discord
Facebook: https://ufl.link/facebook
Instagram: https://ufl.link/instagram
Twitter: https://ufl.link/twitter
TikTok: https://ufl.link/tiktok

Stay tuned for updates via our website ⬇️
https://www.uflgame.com/
⠀
#UFL #strikerz #UFLnews #UFLgame
